asset.description: A perfect place to create a masterpiece with room to share! The Art Easel Desk is a desk with plenty of storage, plus a sturdy easel with a supply shelf and art clip. For more information, visit http://www.step2.com/p/Art-Easel-Desk

transcripts: Stretch your dollar farther and watch your kids creativity soar with the Art Easel Desk from Step2. It's like getting two activity centers in one. There's plenty to keep your little artists busy. On one side we have an adorable little art desk with a work space for one child to color, draw, or paint and a handy storage area fro markers and coloring books. Plus, the desktop lifts up to reveal more storage space. Meanwhile, on the other side, another child can use the standing easel to create his own masterpiece. The dry erase board includes a clip to hang the paper or poster board and a tray fro markers and crayons. The Art Easel Desk offers same sturdiness and stability I've come to expect from Step2. It's the perfect opportunity for two kids to work independently on creative projects while still enjoying one another's comfort.
